ty services; non-destructive testing of concrete and testing facilities for building materials; training programs for masons, site supervisors, and engineers on good construction practices; mobile concrete lab services; field visits by qualified civil engineers; educating individual household builders on various aspects of building material and construction; and other customer specific services. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1942 and is based in Jamnagar, India."}}